Contents:
Discover new ways to use scikit-learn pipelines to automate the machine learning workflow.
Combine two text columns to create one feature.
Use a pipeline to transform features using a TF-IDF vectorizer and fit a logistic regression model to the transformed features.
Add a grid search to the pipeline to find the optimal hyperparameter configuration
Use different performance evaluation techniques in scikit-learn
Repeat the above steps using a decision tree
Compare the performances of using a logistic regression model vs. a decision tree for this problem.
